name: Ubud Champuan Ride Walk
description: This Camphuan ridge walk is the best place for you to experience the trekking activity.It's more than only trekking hiking trail,through its path will accompany you  to explore  Ubud in amazing natural side. You will feel a peaceful atmosphere attack your mind after entering this ridge.You may say this place is like the heaven of beauty with full of romantic impression in every single view.
